Enjoy this 30 minute all-levels flow brought to you by @thebalancedbachelorette 🧘‍♀️ 

TBB provides everything you’ll need for a relaxing yoga class right to your hotel or Airbnb. All classes can be tailored to meet the needs and requests of your group. Hangover, or lack thereof 😉 

Heading to Scottsdale for your BACH? You can book a class with them on the BACH app!

node.text:
☀️ BACH Summer Pro-tip ☀️ The Gulch is THE neighborhood to explore during your summer Nash Bash, but who will guide you through its chic hotels, high-end fashion boutiques, and trendsetting restaurants?

📸  Christy of @photowalknashville will not only capture over 50 stunning Instas of your gorgeous group, she'll also point out the best coffee shops, ice cream parlors, and give you the inside scoop 🍦 on all things Nashville.

📝  So here's the tip: book your Insta-worthy Mural Tour in the BACH app for early in your trip, and get all the perfect recs suited for your crew to round out your FOMO-free weekend in Music City. The most consistent feedback we get for this experience is that the groups wish they had more time to "hang out" with the host. So make sure you get to hang with Christy and let her guide not only your next Instagram posts, but also your perfect Nash Bash weekend!

Also, be mindful of when in your itinerary you book your tour. You know, like not when the sun is beaming down on your group after you've pounded 2 cases of Claws. 😂 💅 Book early in the app so you get your preferred time slots!

#bacheloretteparty #BACHparty #nashville #thegulch #gulch #nashbash #summer #bridetobe2021 #bridetobe2022 #maidofhonor #murals

node.text:
☀️ BACH Summer Giveaway ☀️ Okay BACH Fam, let's start the holiday weekend with our two favorite things: wine, and more wine! You've been loving our rosé for the bride-to-be so much that we've added white wine to our collection—so now you can celebrate the entire BACH crew! We'll send 6 winners a 12-pack that includes all 6 designs. Here's how to win:

1️⃣ Like this post and follow us
2️⃣ Tag your friends in the comments below
3️⃣ Tell us which can fits you the most (see the 6 designs in the photos above). Winners will be notified Tuesday!

🛍️ Shop our delicious rosé and white wine packs for your BACH party! Just tap the "BACH Wine" highlight on our main profile page and swipe up to check out your ordering options. 🇺🇸 🎆 Have a SAFE and exciting holiday weekend, and don't forget to keep rolling out your party plans in our app during all your OOO glory.

#rosé #roséallday #roseallday #whitewine #wine #bachelorettes #bachelorette #BACHparty #bridetobe2021 #bridetobe2022 #bride #bacheloretteparty #girlstrip #cannedcocktails #cannedwine #cocktails #daydrinking #weddingcocktails #drinks #drinks🍹
